{"id":114192,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/10/简讯：智利“愿助中国营救矿工”/","date":"2010-10-17T14:43:18Z","modified":"2010-10-18T19:52:47Z","title":"简讯：智利“愿助中国营救矿工”","content":"<div>\n<p>智利总统皮涅拉说，智利愿对中国和厄瓜多尔的矿难救援工作提供协助。</p>\n<p>中国河南星期六发生的煤矿事故目前尚有16人受困；厄瓜多尔的另一起矿难则有两人失踪。</p>\n<p>皮涅拉说，智利从圣何塞铜矿事件中吸取了许多教训，当中包括要做好对矿工生命的保障。</p>\n<p>他祝愿两国被困矿工能逃出生天。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/WSd5hhI9SAlxlQXvt3Kv0OwQfek/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/WSd5hhI9SAlxlQXvt3Kv0OwQfek/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/WSd5hhI9SAlxlQXvt3Kv0OwQfek/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/WSd5hhI9SAlxlQXvt3Kv0OwQfek/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=LVKxg5_HtXA:crewRlbfH14:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=LVKxg5_HtXA:crewRlbfH14:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=LVKxg5_HtXA:crewRlbfH14:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=LVKxg5_HtXA:crewRlbfH14:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=LVKxg5_HtXA:crewRlbfH14:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=LVKxg5_HtXA:crewRlbfH14:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/LVKxg5_HtXA\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwe